        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 81–87. Heptodonta eugenia Chaudoir, 1865: 81, 83, 85–87—♂, Laos, Oudomxay, La (JWCW): 81—habitus, 83— head, 85—lateral body, 86—aedeagus in left lateral aspect, 87—aedeagus in right lateral aspect; 82, 84—♀, Khammouane, Nakai (JWCW): 82—habitus, 84—head. Scales: 81–85 = 1 mm, 86–87 = 0.5 mm." ;
